headline: Keysight Receives Frost & Sullivan's 2025 Global Company of the Year Award for Excellence in 6G Test and Measurement
summary: Frost & Sullivan is proud to recognize Keysight Technologies with the 2025 Global Company of the Year award in the 6G test and measurement industry. This honor highlights Keysight's exceptional performance in innovation, strategic execution, and market leadership, affirming its role as a trusted partner driving the global shift from 5G to 6G.
